And here we have the exhaust system ,.its a quirky feature that relieves pain but can be used for laughter, and can also make somebody really , really angry . Hehe 😀

The nose hairs while very quirky , is actually a very good feature. But there is a downside. If you don't trim them you eventually look like Chewbacca,..hehe😀....so that gets a Doug Score of 5.
